# Fallback Strategy

If the preferred model is unavailable:

Architecture

Claude Opus → GPT-5.5

Research

GPT-5.5 → Claude Opus

Implementation

Composer 2.5 → GPT-5.5

Never stop execution because one model is unavailable.

Choose the closest equivalent.

Only then begin implementation.